BEGIN:VEVENT
UID:L9JwiVLaSVVr_NPQdQF6p
SUMMARY:Saturday Flow + Yin Yoga
DTSTAMP:20260314T153800Z
DTSTART:20260314T150000Z
DESCRIPTION:This class will leave you feeling physically and energetically 
	balanced! Practice begins with 30 minutes of dynamic movement. Emphasis on
	 synchronizing breath with poses to create an intense internal heat and pu
	rifying sweat that detoxifies the body. The last 30 minutes of practice\, 
	poses are held for several minutes focusing on finding increased mobility 
	in the joints – spine\, hips and shoulders. Each pose will aim to access t
	he deep layers of fascia to release tension holding areas on the body. \\*
	Drop-in for $25\n\nhttps://seatoday.6amcity.com/events/#/details/saturday-
	flow-yin-yoga/17288448/2026-03-14T00\n\nFrom SEAtoday - Sports & Outdoors
URL:https://seatoday.6amcity.com/events/#/details/saturday-flow-yin-yoga/17
	288448/2026-03-14T00
X-CALRIPPER-SOURCE:seatoday-sports
CATEGORIES:SEAtoday - Sports & Outdoors
TRANSP:TRANSPARENT
DURATION:PT1H
END:VEVENT
