DESCRIPTION:A Kirkland and Eastside tradition is put on my Running Company\
	, Cascade Stride. This is the run that everyone talks about weeks after th
	e race! Signing up early saves LOTS of money. Come join Lake Washington Ph
	ysical Therapy and Cascade Stride by "wearing the green" for a fun family 
	fun run. The event will start and end at the Marina Park in Kirkland\, WA.
